RelatedSentence: KUWAIT CITY , May 19 : The Philippine Embassy line with its continued effort for to better serve all Filipino nationals has announced on weekend the arrival of two new officials to augment the embassy personnel .

Philippine Ambassador to Kuwait Lamberto V Monsanto introduced First Secretary and Consul Jabbar Adiong and Third Secretary and Vice Consul Shiena Tesorero to the leaders of various Filipino organizations in Kuwait who were welcomed by the community .
